de.be4.classicalb.core.parser.analysis
Class PreParserASTPrinter

java.lang.Object
  de.be4.classicalb.core.preparser.analysis.AnalysisAdapter
      de.be4.classicalb.core.preparser.analysis.ReversedDepthFirstAdapter
          de.be4.classicalb.core.parser.analysis.PreParserASTPrinter
All Implemented Interfaces:
Analysis, Switch
public class PreParserASTPrinter
extends ReversedDepthFirstAdapter

Text display of the AST, with (optionally) color output. To print the AST we do a reverse depth first traversal. We do this because it is easier to know which element is the last child in any node. This makes it easier to do nice indenting.
